
    <div style="padding:15px 15px 600px;font-size:30px">
        <p><b>This example demonstrates how to slide down a navbar when the user starts to scroll the page.</b></p>
        <p>Scroll down this frame to see the effect!</p>
        <p>Scroll to the top to hide the navbar.</p>
        <p>Lorem ipsum dolor dummy text sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut
